sentences: Eufradis Rodriguez, (born October 28, 1992), better known by his stage name Euro, is a Dominican-American rapper signed to Young Money Entertainment, and was born in the Dominican Republic.
Euro released a mixtape called July, on July 31, 2014.
In 2014 Euro attended a street heat production free-styling back and forth with Cory Gunz, showing off his extensive rap skills.
Euro announced that he will be releasing his debut mixtape, Don't Expect Nothing, with a release date during 2014.
